      "role": "user",
      "content": "I don't really get the metaphor. Can you just explain the actual physics of the internal stress distribution? Like, if there is a bending moment on the beam, where exactly does the tension happen and how does the steel actually handle that force? Just keep it technical please.",
      "source": "evaluator"
